{"tid":1694151,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"樹仁又有回應！","createTime":"2019-11-05T03:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T03:35:03.000Z","uid":266261,"like":115,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"82b2c10d8456cd7b87c778e9a8dd9b38c3c03a53","tid":1694151,"uid":266261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:51:08.000Z","msg":"致各位同學和老師：<br />\n<br />\n上周六一位同學於港島區的公眾活動中懷疑遭催淚煙彈擊中，身體嚴重燒傷，目前仍然留醫接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n作為教育工作者，關顧學生是我們的天職。校方昨天下午已去信警務處處長，要求處方在七日內提供有關今次事件的一切資料，以釐清事實，作進一步後續跟進。（見附件）<br />\n<br />\n我們在此再次呼籲同學須注意自身安全，留意隨時發生的衝突情況，遠離暴力。<br />\n<br />\n胡懷中<br />\n2019年11月5日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giiF5jP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiiF5jP.png&h=d1e27d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcZeqjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcZeqjQ.png&h=aa3d8d00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bab0b4df1df52b618b2c7ab28ecaf995df3fbfb","tid":1694151,"uid":106336,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"大學榜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbaa6909957a9ec7a7d090c0fb2077e87d6b450","tid":1694151,"uid":55162,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"係樹仁身上見到咩係關心學生"},{"pid":"9bc107576e84783bb7a6b665892ee9bdf7944c12","tid":1694151,"uid":311985,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"真係好撚型！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好過其他U唔肯出聲"},{"pid":"ed2559a5846c0b93bbe841b6db034f6e646724f0","tid":1694151,"uid":103826,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;作為教育工作者，關顧學生是我們的天職。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6174799393c95e91fab672341c98467dac0c52e8","tid":1694151,"uid":98407,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,